---
title: Chermoula Chicken & Roast Veggie Toss with Lemon Yoghurt Dressing & Roasted Almonds
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their chicken? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy chermoula spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Finish it off with a bed of roasted veggies and a sprinkling of crunchy almonds for an outstanding pairing of flavours.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-chicken-roast-veggie-toss-1e87b6a7.jpg
